    "description": "You're now a full-fledged member of the Yolo Space Hacker team.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis is your chance to get to grips with the new equipment:<br />\r\n- electric snipes<br />\r\n- cyber binoculars<br />\r\n- parachute<br />\r\n- drone<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn 3D TPS, alternate between infiltration and hacking into cameras and servers, using real tools and real security holes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChain missions together: <br />\r\n- disabling a satellite jamming site<br />\r\n- infiltration of a military camp<br />\r\n- Bahamas Bank penetration test<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou'll need to hone your OSInt skills, prepare a trojan, and carry out targeted phishing to penetrate the bank, and open the vaults discreetly...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnd if you don't have enough, or if it's all too easy, switch at will between beginner and expert modes.<br />\r\nAnd find the bonus servers - they're everywhere.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGood Hacks",
